descriptionHtml:
Rhodaa is a peer to peer electronic car rental platform currently operating in Egypt and Sudan. We dignify ourselves in achieving a balance between customer and vehicle-owner satisfaction so that everyone's a winner.
By providing you with a large list of distinctive options at competitive and affordable prices, with access to quick and safe profits for the vehicle owners, and by giving them all the guarantees for the safety of their cars, Rhodaa becomes a profit-making, safe haven for all car owners and renters!
Whether you own a car or want to rent one, Rhodaa benefits everybody!
Car Owners:
* ﻿Got a car? Looking to make more income? Look no further because you can put your car up for rent
* ﻿﻿A selection of insurance companies with worthy packages to choose from
* ﻿﻿An instant-responding professional team working all around the clock to serve the clients of the company
Car Renters:
* ﻿﻿A vast range of vehicles for our customers to choose from, at competitive prices that suit all wages!
* ﻿﻿Find ease and convenience renting a car with Rhodaa, no matter where you are in the world
* ﻿﻿Don't worry about insurance, all our cars are fully insured!
* ﻿﻿An instant-responding professional team working all around the clock to serve the clients of the company

Rhodaa acts as mediator between two people who have a common goal. So, hurry up and get on board!

creator: H AND M LEADING EDGE
descriptionHtml:
Rhodaa is a dynamic and innovative peer-to-peer car-sharing platform that provides a seamless and cost-effective solution for individuals in Egypt.

Our mission is to bridge the gap between car owners and renters, creating a mutually beneficial relationship that is centered on customer satisfaction.

We believe in providing a seamless, personalized experience for all our customers, from the easy-to-use platform to 24/7 support, and comprehensive insurance coverage.

Our strict vetting process for car owners and renters ensures that all users feel confident and secure while using the Rhodaa platform.

Rhodaa offers a diverse range of vehicles for renters, providing a more personalized and convenient rental experience at a fraction of the cost of traditional rental services.

For car owners, Rhodaa provides an opportunity to monetize their underutilized vehicles, generating passive income and offsetting the costs of car ownership.

At Rhodaa, we are dedicated to creating a sustainable future through the power of car sharing. Whether you need a car for a road trip, weekend getaway, or daily commute, Rhodaa has a vehicle for every occasion.
descriptionShort: Rhodaa is peer to peer car rental platform in Egypt.
